## Data reliability
* API fallback system (provider redundancy)
* rate limit handling + retry queue
* caching layer for repeated financial queries
* background refresh jobs for market data
* stale data detection
* timestamped data validity checks

## Observability
* request tracing (per user session)
* LLM output logging
* hallucination detection logs
* API error analytics dashboard
* performance monitoring
* data freshness metrics

## Financial safety layer
* disclaimer injection pipeline
* uncertainty labeling (“data incomplete”)
* confidence scoring for responses
* anomaly detection in generated numbers

Finance must never pretend certainty.

